overview: Watch Garth as he hitches-hikes 3000 kms from Melbourne to Cairns, gets stranded on the side of the road for 8 hours, spend one night in a cemetery, one night on a pile of sand at a construction site, and one night at a bus stop! All in the name of adventure!
tagline: Watch Garth as he hitches-hikes 3000 kms from Melbourne to Cairns.
title: Garth Goes Hitch-Hiking
